          <div class="pop"><img src="/assets/custom/ubc/tagxedo.jpg"></div>
        </div>
        <p>This activity is for you and your mentor. Create a word cloud that tells a bit about who you are. Tagxedo (www.tagxedo.com) uses words, colours, shapes and fonts to create fun images.</p>

        <p>Watch this video to get ideas for your word cloud and learn how to use Tagxedo:</p>

        <div style="padding:4px;border:1px solid black;text-align:center;overflow:hidden">
        <p>Tagxedo Presentation (2 videos)<br>
        <a href="http://youtu.be/4z7qTziwMqQ" target="_blank">http://youtu.be/4z7qTziwMqQ</a><br>
        <a href="http://youtu.be/rOciNkGzZUU" target="_blank">http://youtu.be/rOciNkGzZUU</a>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align:center"><div class="pop" style="width:100%;display:inline-block"><img src="/assets/custom/ubc/questions.jpg" style="width:80%"></div></div>

        <p>Choose any of these questions to come up with words to put in your word cloud. You do
